{
  "id": "RAW_74457409",
  "title": "最近产品用户规模和收入都新高了，我感恩自己遇到的一切",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247500274&idx=1&sn=efc38aabad154628d4c98dc1d4a54b2e",
  "date": "2026-01-07 16:04:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">还记得吗，上个月我的Raphael ( <a href=\"https://raphael.app\" target=\"_blank\">https://raphael.app</a> )重新起飞了&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247499945&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2369eeff98dffb1decc1890cd229a772&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"从100万月活跌下来之后，我让Raphael AI 再次起飞：没投广告，只做了4件小事\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">从100万月活跌下来之后，我让Raphael AI 再次起飞：没投广告，只做了4件小事</a>&nbsp;，当时我们约定：等到12月数据出来，肯定是新高。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈哈，没错！<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">12月的数据刚刚出来，果然是新高。月活达到了145万，环比提升119.41%</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">看到这个图还挺感慨的。Raphael域名注册时间是2025年1月10日，今天是2026年1月8日，只差2天，就是一年。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">一年，我给了自己一份特别满意的答卷！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100016621\" data-ratio=\"0.6333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa9c462e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGricVh8vI2bBeYtgauPNYJBWv1qhKafs88VQJPS8bjY4VB5A5ic0I60VVN1eDeQFB9W96wVicE0EzGw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚才大树兄弟问我新产品怎么样，我有点不好意思，因为Raphael数据天天涨，我最近都没怎么管新产品了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近心情特别好。一个月前，程前团队重新采访我的时候（下面的视频6分20秒开始），Raphael已经稍微有点重新起飞的势头了。采访的时候他们问我Raphael这款的产品收入，当时Raphael的收入只有每天1000美金。我也没想到节目播出的时候，一个月就涨了那么多了。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">由于网站数据是公开的，毫无秘密可言，有很多朋友和同行都已经注意到了Raphael，来问我具体怎么做的。我这里统一回答我的感想吧，仅代表我个人、此时此刻的认知，不一定对，欢迎讨论。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size:20px;\">第一因素：运气</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不用怀疑，我是一个非常非常幸运的人。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我从小学四年级开始编程，从小就喜欢做产品。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">十年前，我幸运地被猎豹移动收购，师从傅盛老师，贴身学习产品方法论、学习做海外工具产品、学习AI。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我现在的合伙人、员工非常给力，万里挑一。感兴趣的话你可以参考这一篇末尾<a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247500248&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=5db881386dcacf5f25ed70eaccc7dbbe&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"不加班、不PUA，还给全员发 iPhone 17 Pro Max：创业一年，我们居然没死\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">不加班、不PUA，还给全员发 iPhone 17 Pro Max：创业一年，我们居然没死</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我还在生财有术结识了很多不知道为啥就是特别爱帮助我的兄弟姐妹。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我还爱学习。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">更幸运的是，在2023年这个世界上出现了一个叫“AI编程”的新物种，我比绝大多数人都更早地拥抱了它。<a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247498933&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=fa72632c3ed7141c0dfd6069f53e2cf0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致｜对话刘小排\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致｜对话刘小排</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">想要集齐这么多幸运的要素可真是不容易。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我感恩自己遇到的一切。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有时候看到周围其他人抱怨环境，我都觉得自己好幸运。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">《了不起的盖茨比》开篇有一句类似的话，“<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">每逢你想要指责任何人的时候，你就记住，这个世界上所有的人，并不是个个都有过你拥有的那些优越条件。</span>” &nbsp;我常常想，这说的不就是我吗……</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">谢谢你们。谢谢这个世界。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size:20px;\">第二因素：我的恩师傅盛告诉我——做好产品，其他的一切都会纷至沓来。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">海外产品圈子的朋友、认识我的朋友可能知道，Raphael这款产品中间出现过一些失误，被坏人钻了点空子，导致了流量被人抢了不少。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">实话说，Raphael要重新爬起来并不容易的，比从零开始还难。直到现在，我都还没完全从一年前的失误里走出来，否则用户量会更大。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是我一直坚信：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">做好产品，其他的一切都会纷至沓来</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">邪不胜正</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">整整一年的低调坚守，排除噪音，躲进小楼成一统，管他冬夏与春秋，只求把产品打磨得越来越好。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我终于等到了Raphael重新开花的时候。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">谢谢傅盛老师的教诲！</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://raphael.app\" target=\"_blank\">https://raphael.app</a>&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100016623\" data-ratio=\"0.5218045112781955\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2660\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1070ecbf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGricVh8vI2bBeYtgauPNYJBW47s7SjzM3VLnzE2wfpuxejwI1vOu2aqUCqib2E76jBDW1NmJhwGyXg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我会在2026年继续努力，不辜负整个世界对我的祝福、不浪费我的天赋和运气！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">放心，下个月Raphael还会再创新高的！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">谢谢你看到这里、谢谢你对我的祝福和关注！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 32px 0px !important;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">附录：如果你想了解我更多</span></span></p>\n    <ul style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;list-style-type:circle;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 1.6em;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0px !important;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;background-color: #faf9f7 !important;padding: 20px 24px 56px 24px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2025年3月，我一个人用Cursor做出的Raphael，刚刚起飞 ：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(125, 144, 169);text-decoration: none;-webkit-user-drag: none;cursor: default;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247497767&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=39158f8611e5677a5003868458d674d6&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"我用Cursor做的产品，月活超过100万了\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">我用Cursor做的产品，月活超过100万了</span></a></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0px !important;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2025年4月，我开始和生财有术一起做SCAI孵化器&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" class=\"js_darkmode__10\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;color:rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;letter-spacing:-0.005em;font-size:18px;line-height:1.75 !important;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:700px;text-align:left;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(125, 144, 169);text-decoration: none;-webkit-user-drag: none;cursor: default;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247497860&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=86eb907a4d5c598db691a3adcd67179e&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"我正式开始做孵化器了\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">我正式开始做孵化器了</span></a></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0px !important;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" class=\"js_darkmode__11\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;color:rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;letter-spacing:-0.005em;font-size:18px;line-height:1.75 !important;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:700px;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2025年5月，放弃Cursor，使用Claude Code打主力&nbsp;</span><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(125, 144, 169);text-decoration: none;-webkit-user-drag: none;cursor: default;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247497883&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=9afed7fbe937f0208293ad75fdc